description:
FileTPM: Metadata table describing Ericsson-specific TPM (Transmission Performance Monitoring) data files, including timestamp, location, cell identifier, and file version information.
- dateTime: Timestamp of data file creation.
- Area_Name: Name of the geographical area covered by the cell.
- CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site.
- Id2: Redundant cell identifier (possibly a backup or alternative ID).
- Id3:  Unknown identifier (likely internal or unused).
- Id4: Unknown identifier (likely internal or unused).
- vsDataType: Specifies the data type as Ericsson-specific TPM data.
- vsDataFormatVersion: Specifies the version of the Ericsson-specific attributes format.
- FileTPM.fileTPMId: Unique identifier of the TPM data file.
